  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong> into thick slices</p>\r\n<p>Lay them out on a grill tray (use tin foil to avoid mess!)</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle them with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Preheat&nbsp;your grill to high (for step 5)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>linguine</strong> to a large pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook the linguine over a high heat for 8 min or until it retains a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain the linguine and reserve approx. 500ml of the <strong>starchy cooking water&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and grate (or finely chop) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>shallots</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>Italian hard&nbsp;cheese&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grate or very finely chop the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the sliced <strong>portobello mushrooms&nbsp;</strong>under the grill for 10 min or until the mushrooms are browned and caramelised</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a high heat<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>shallot</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chestnut&nbsp;mushrooms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Crumble the<strong>&nbsp;vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;</strong>into the pan&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cook over a medium-high heat for 5-7 min or until everything is browned and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>linguine</strong> and approx. 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span>&nbsp;of the reserved <strong>starchy </strong><strong>cooking&nbsp;water</strong> to the mushroom pan and mix well</p>\r\n<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir in half the<strong> parsley</strong>, half the grilled <strong>portobellos</strong> and half the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Stir in the <strong>Greek-style&nbsp;</strong><strong>yoghurt</strong> and season generously with <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/399.step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Check that the linguine is not too dry - if it is, add a splash or two of the remaining <strong>starchy </strong><strong>cooking&nbsp;water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Serve the linguine, garnishing with the remaining<strong> parsley</strong>, <strong>grilled</strong>&nbsp;<strong>portobellos</strong> and <strong>cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
